    {
      "Text": "Security update for Mesa",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for Mesa fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2023-45913: NULL pointer dereference via dri2GetGlxDrawableFromXDrawableId() (bsc#1222040).\n- CVE-2023-45919: Buffer over-read in glXQueryServerString() (bsc#1222041).\n- CVE-2023-45922: Segmentation violation in __glXGetDrawableAttribute() (bsc#1222042).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
